## Overview

The Soft Aware API provides programmatic access to our AI-powered platform, enabling developers to:

- **Authenticate users** and manage accounts
- **Integrate AI capabilities** into applications (chat, code generation, vision)
- **Manage subscriptions** and billing programmatically
- **Access credit-based services** for AI operations
- **Build custom dashboards** and admin tools
- **Automate workflows** via webhooks

### Key Features

✅ **RESTful Architecture** — Standard HTTP methods (GET, POST, PUT, DELETE)  
✅ **JWT Authentication** — Secure, stateless token-based auth  
✅ **API Key Support** — Alternative authentication for server-to-server calls  
✅ **Multi-Provider AI** — OpenAI, Anthropic, Google Gemini, local Ollama, and more  
✅ **Credit System** — Pay-as-you-go pricing with transparent costs  
✅ **CORS Enabled** — Works from browsers, mobile apps, and servers  
✅ **Webhook Support** — Real-time notifications for events  

