## API Endpoints

### Authentication & Users

#### `POST /auth/register`
Create a new user account.

**Request:**
```json
{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "securepass123",
  "teamName": "My Team" // optional
}
```

**Response:** `201 Created`
```json
{
  "accessToken": "jwt_token_here",
  "user": { "id": "...", "email": "..." },
  "team": { "id": "...", "name": "My Team" },
  "activationKey": "USER-XXXX"
}
```

**Errors:**
- `400` — Email already registered
- `400` — Invalid email format
- `400` — Password too short (min 8 chars)

---

#### `POST /auth/login`
Authenticate a user and receive a JWT token.

**Request:**
```json
{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "securepass123",
  "rememberMe": false  // true = 30 day token, false = 1 hour
}
```

**Response:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "accessToken": "eyJhbGci...",
  "token": "eyJhbGci...",
  "expiresIn": "1h",
  "user": {
    "id": "uuid",
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "name": "John Doe",
    "phone": "+27821234567",
    "role": "admin"
  },
  "team": {
    "id": "team-uuid",
    "name": "ACME Corp",
    "role": "ADMIN"
  }
}
```

**Errors:**
- `400` — Invalid email or password

---

#### `POST /auth/refresh`
Refresh an existing JWT token before it expires.

**Request:**
```json
{
  "accessToken": "current_token_here"
}
```

**Response:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "accessToken": "new_token_here"
}
```

---

### Profile Management

All profile endpoints require JWT authentication (`Authorization: Bearer <token>`).

#### `GET /profile`
Get the authenticated user's complete profile including team, subscription, and credits.

**Response:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "user": {
    "id": "user-uuid",
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "name": "John Doe",
    "phone": "+27821234567",
    "avatarUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/avatar.jpg",
    "createdAt": "2026-01-15T10:30:00Z"
  },
  "team": {
    "id": "team-uuid",
    "name": "ACME Corp",
    "role": "ADMIN"
  },
  "subscription": {
    "id": "sub-uuid",
    "status": "ACTIVE",
    "tier": "TEAM",
    "planName": "Team Plan",
    "currentPeriodEnd": "2026-03-15T00:00:00Z"
  },
  "credits": {
    "balance": 15000,
    "totalPurchased": 20000,
    "totalUsed": 5000
  }
}
```

---

#### `PUT /profile`
Update the authenticated user's profile.

**Request:**
```json
{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "phone": "+27821234567",
  "avatarUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/new-avatar.jpg"
}
```

**Response:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "message": "Profile updated",
  "user": {
    "id": "user-uuid",
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "name": "Jane Doe",
    "phone": "+27821234567",
    "avatarUrl": "https://cdn.example.com/new-avatar.jpg",
    "updatedAt": "2026-02-28T14:20:00Z"
  }
}
```

---

#### `POST /profile/change-password`
Change the authenticated user's password.

**Request:**
```json
{
  "currentPassword": "oldpassword123",
  "newPassword": "newsecurepass456"
}
```

**Response:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "message": "Password changed successfully"
}
```

**Errors:**
- `400` — Current password is incorrect
- `400` — New password too short

