### Subscriptions

#### `GET /subscriptions/plans`
Get all available subscription plans.

**Authentication:** None required (public endpoint)

**Response:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "plans": [
    {
      "id": "plan-personal",
      "tier": "PERSONAL",
      "name": "Personal Plan",
      "description": "Perfect for individual developers",
      "priceMonthly": 29900,
      "priceMonthlyDisplay": "R299",
      "priceAnnually": 299900,
      "priceAnnuallyDisplay": "R2,999",
      "trialDays": 14,
      "features": {
        "maxUsers": 1,
        "maxAgents": 5,
        "maxDevices": 3,
        "cloudSync": true,
        "vault": false,
        "prioritySupport": false
      },
      "isActive": true
    },
    {
      "id": "plan-team",
      "tier": "TEAM",
      "name": "Team Plan",
      "description": "Collaboration for small teams",
      "priceMonthly": 99900,
      "priceMonthlyDisplay": "R999",
      "priceAnnually": 999900,
      "priceAnnuallyDisplay": "R9,999",
      "trialDays": 14,
      "features": {
        "maxUsers": 10,
        "maxAgents": 50,
        "maxDevices": 20,
        "cloudSync": true,
        "vault": true,
        "prioritySupport": true
      },
      "isActive": true
    }
  ]
}
```

---

#### `GET /subscriptions/current`
Get the current user's active subscription.

**Authentication:** JWT required

**Response:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "subscription": {
    "id": "sub-uuid",
    "status": "ACTIVE",
    "currentPeriodStart": "2026-02-01T00:00:00Z",
    "currentPeriodEnd": "2026-03-01T00:00:00Z",
    "trialEndsAt": null,
    "cancelledAt": null,
    "plan": {
      "tier": "TEAM",
      "name": "Team Plan",
      "priceMonthlyDisplay": "R999"
    }
  },
  "team": {
    "id": "team-uuid",
    "name": "ACME Corp"
  }
}
```

**Response when no subscription:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "subscription": null,
  "status": "NO_SUBSCRIPTION",
  "team": {
    "id": "team-uuid",
    "name": "ACME Corp"
  }
}
```

---

#### `POST /subscriptions/start-trial`
Start a free trial subscription.

**Authentication:** JWT required

**Request:**
```json
{
  "tier": "TEAM"
}
```

**Response:** `201 Created`
```json
{
  "message": "Trial started successfully",
  "subscription": {
    "id": "sub-uuid",
    "status": "TRIAL",
    "trialEndsAt": "2026-03-14T00:00:00Z"
  }
}
```

**Errors:**
- `400` — Team already has an active subscription

---

#### `POST /subscriptions/change-plan`
Change the subscription plan.

**Authentication:** JWT required (ADMIN role)

**Request:**
```json
{
  "tier": "ENTERPRISE",
  "billingCycle": "annually"
}
```

**Response:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "message": "Plan changed successfully",
  "subscription": {
    "id": "sub-uuid",
    "status": "ACTIVE",
    "plan": {
      "tier": "ENTERPRISE",
      "name": "Enterprise Plan"
    }
  }
}
```

**Errors:**
- `403` — Only team admins can change plans

---

#### `POST /subscriptions/cancel`
Cancel the current subscription.

**Authentication:** JWT required (ADMIN role)

**Response:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "message": "Subscription cancelled. Access will continue until end of billing period.",
  "subscription": {
    "id": "sub-uuid",
    "status": "CANCELLED",
    "cancelledAt": "2026-02-28T14:00:00Z"
  },
  "accessEndsAt": "2026-03-01T00:00:00Z"
}
```

