### Team Management

#### `POST /teams/:id/invite`
Invite a user to join your team.

**Authentication:** JWT required (ADMIN role)

**Request:**
```json
{
  "email": "newmember@example.com",
  "role": "OPERATOR"
}
```

**Roles:**
- `ADMIN` — Full access
- `ARCHITECT` — Can configure AI and agents
- `OPERATOR` — Standard user access
- `AUDITOR` — Read-only access

**Response:** `201 Created`
```json
{
  "invite": {
    "id": "invite-uuid",
    "email": "newmember@example.com",
    "role": "OPERATOR",
    "createdAt": "2026-02-28T15:00:00Z"
  }
}
```

---

#### `PUT /teams/:id/members/:userId`
Update a team member's role.

**Authentication:** JWT required (ADMIN role)

**Request:**
```json
{
  "role": "ARCHITECT"
}
```

**Response:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "member": {
    "userId": "user-uuid",
    "teamId": "team-uuid",
    "role": "ARCHITECT"
  }
}
```

---

#### `DELETE /teams/:id/members/:userId`
Remove a member from the team.

**Authentication:** JWT required (ADMIN role)

**Response:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Member removed from team"
}
```

