## Updates System

The Updates system manages software product registrations, update distribution, client heartbeat tracking, module management, and remote control. All endpoints are prefixed with `/updates/`.

### System Overview

The Updates API supports:
- **Software Registry** — Track multiple software products with unique keys
- **Update Distribution** — Upload, manage, and distribute versioned update packages
- **Client Heartbeats** — Monitor connected client installations in real-time
- **Remote Control** — Force logout, send messages to connected clients
- **Module Management** — Track software modules and developer assignments
- **Password Reset** — OTP-based email password recovery

---

