```

🔒🛡️ **Admin only.**

#### Client Status

Computed from heartbeat recency:

| Status | Condition |
|--------|----------|
| `online` | < 5 minutes ago |
| `recent` | < 24 hours ago |
| `inactive` | < 7 days ago |
| `offline` | ≥ 7 days ago |

#### Client Actions (PUT)

```json
{ "id": 15, "action": "block", "reason": "Unauthorized" }
{ "id": 15, "action": "unblock" }
{ "id": 15, "action": "force_logout" }
{ "id": 15, "action": "send_message", "message": "Please update" }
```

