### Password Reset (Updates)

```
POST /updates/password_reset    — Request OTP
POST /updates/verify_otp        — Verify OTP
POST /updates/reset_password    — Execute reset
```

All public. Three-step flow:

**Step 1 — Request OTP:**
```bash
curl -X POST https://api.softaware.net.za/updates/password_reset \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"identifier": "admin@softaware.co.za"}'
```
```json
{ "success": true, "message": "If the account exists, a reset code has been sent." }
```

**Step 2 — Verify OTP:**
```bash
curl -X POST https://api.softaware.net.za/updates/verify_otp \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"identifier": "admin@softaware.co.za", "otp": "123456"}'
```

**Step 3 — Reset Password:**
```bash
curl -X POST https://api.softaware.net.za/updates/reset_password \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"identifier": "admin@softaware.co.za", "otp": "123456", "new_password": "newSecurePass"}'
```

